{"operationName":"getMainchainPositions","variables":{"eth_address":"0x7e4abd63a7c8314cc28d388303472353d884f292","chain":"mainchain"},"query":"query getMainchainPositions($eth_address: String, $chain: String) {
  getMainchainPositions(eth_address: $eth_address, chain: $chain) {
    id
    direction
    average_price
    average_spread
    average_leverage
    long_shares
    short_shares
    timestamp
    value
    value_weight
    total_return
    total_return_percent
    liquidation_timestamp
    market {
      id
      name
      type
      symbol
      close
      change
      change_percent
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
"}

{"operationName":"getMainchainPositions","variables":{"eth_address":"0x7e4abd63a7c8314cc28d388303472353d884f292","chain":"mainchain"},"query":"query getMainchainPositions($eth_address: String, $chain: String) {
  getMainchainPositions(eth_address: $eth_address, chain: $chain) {
    id
    direction
    average_price
    average_spread
    average_leverage
    long_shares
    short_shares
    timestamp
    value
    value_weight
    total_return
    total_return_percent
    liquidation_timestamp
    market {
      id
      name
      type
      symbol
      close
      change
      change_percent
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
"}
